+From 3145f9ae33ed74d067cee36660b29b8b00ec1160 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
+From: "Antonio A. Russo" <aarusso@nyxk.com.br>
+Date: Sun, 5 Oct 2025 20:19:57 -0300
+Subject: [PATCH 0/6] stynx frontend/backend modernization
+
+This series introduces environment scaffolding, modern Angular patterns, and the admin user management console imported from PORM, aligning the base project with shared conventions.
+
+Antonio A. Russo (6):
+  chore(env): add backend .env.example with all relevant variables
+  refactor(frontend): split inline templates and styles into separate
+    files
+  refactor(frontend): migrate *ngIf/*ngFor to Angular @if/@for syntax
+  refactor(frontend): migrate dependency injection to inject() API
+  feat(admin): integrate user management module from porm with role and
+    tenancy handling
+  docs: update readme and developer guide with modernization steps
+
+-- 
+2.50.1 (Apple Git-155)
+
